---
// Hero section: editorial-style asymmetric layout
---

<section id="home" class="hero-mesh relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="min-h-screen flex items-center pt-28 pb-20 md:pt-36 md:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[color:var(--color-primary)] font-semibold">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[color:var(--color-primary)]"></span>
            We Quest On and On
          </span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="mt-4 md:mt-6 font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-[color:var(--color-midnight)]">
          唯蟹 Team
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 md:mt-8 text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-[color:var(--color-text)] leading-relaxed max-w-md mx-auto">
          一群热爱技术、专注于创造有趣数字世界的伙伴们，用代码书写属于我们自己的故事。
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 md:mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3 md:gap-4">
          <a href="#about" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-3.5 rounded-full bg-[color:var(--color-primary)] text-white font-semibold text-sm shadow-[0_4px_14px_-4px_rgba(0,122,255,0.5)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_20px_-6px_rgba(0,122,255,0.6)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-200">
            认识成员
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-3.5 rounded-full bg-[color:var(--color-bg-card)] text-[color:var(--color-midnight)] font-semibold text-sm shadow-[0_4px_14px_-4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] dark:shadow-[0_4px_14px_-4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_20px_-6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)] dark:hover:shadow-[0_6px_20px_-6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-200">
            查看服务
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
